                          inscription: in Greek, <br />
front, upper arm, running horizontally: Ι ΑΓΙΑ Θ|ΕΟΤΟ|ΚΟϹ [Holy God-Bearer, i.e., the Virgin Mary]; <br />
<br />
front, bottom arm, running vertically: Ο ΑΓΙΟϹ ΠΕ|ΤΡΟ [Saint Peter]<br />
<br />
back, top arm, running horizontally: Ο ΑΡΧ|ΙϹΤΡΑ|ΤΙΓΟ [the chief general, i.e., the Archangel Michael]
                        </li>
                                          
                    
